{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.1","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:1","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.007.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Les Isra\u00e9lites demandent un roi<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-22: cf. Ps 82. De 17:14-20. (1 S 10:17-25. Os 13:10, 11.) \u00c9s 33:22.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Lorsque Samuel devint vieux, il \u00e9tablit ses fils juges sur Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.2","name":"1 Samuel 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.7.17","name":"1 Samuel 7:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.7.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.2","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:2","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Son fils premier-n\u00e9 se nommait Jo\u00ebl, et le second Abija; ils \u00e9taient juges \u00e0 Beer-Sch\u00e9ba.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.3","name":"1 Samuel 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.1","name":"1 Samuel 8:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.3","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:3","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Les fils de Samuel ne march\u00e8rent point sur ses traces; ils se livraient \u00e0 la cupidit\u00e9, recevaient des pr\u00e9sents, et violaient la justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.4","name":"1 Samuel 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.2","name":"1 Samuel 8:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.4","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:4","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Tous les anciens d\u2019Isra\u00ebl s\u2019assembl\u00e8rent, et vinrent aupr\u00e8s de Samuel \u00e0 Rama.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.5","name":"1 Samuel 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.3","name":"1 Samuel 8:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.5","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:5","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ils lui dirent: Voici, tu es vieux, et tes fils ne marchent point sur tes traces; maintenant, \u00e9tablis sur nous un roi pour nous juger, comme il y en a chez toutes les nations.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.6","name":"1 Samuel 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.4","name":"1 Samuel 8:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.6","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:6","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Samuel vit avec d\u00e9plaisir qu\u2019ils disaient: Donne-nous un roi pour nous juger. Et Samuel pria l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.7","name":"1 Samuel 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.5","name":"1 Samuel 8:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.7","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:7","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Samuel: \u00c9coute la voix du peuple dans tout ce qu\u2019il te dira; car ce n\u2019est pas toi qu\u2019ils rejettent, c\u2019est moi qu\u2019ils rejettent, afin que je ne r\u00e8gne plus sur eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.8","name":"1 Samuel 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.6","name":"1 Samuel 8:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.8","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:8","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ils agissent \u00e0 ton \u00e9gard comme ils ont toujours agi depuis que je les ai fait monter d\u2019\u00c9gypte jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce jour; ils m\u2019ont abandonn\u00e9, pour servir d\u2019autres dieux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.9","name":"1 Samuel 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.7","name":"1 Samuel 8:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.9","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:9","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\u00c9coute donc leur voix; mais donne-leur des avertissements, et fais-leur conna\u00eetre le droit du roi qui r\u00e9gnera sur eux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.10","name":"1 Samuel 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.8","name":"1 Samuel 8:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.10","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:10","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Samuel rapporta toutes les paroles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel au peuple qui lui demandait un roi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.11","name":"1 Samuel 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.9","name":"1 Samuel 8:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.11","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:11","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il dit: Voici quel sera le droit du roi qui r\u00e9gnera sur vous. Il prendra vos fils, et il les mettra sur ses chars et parmi ses cavaliers, afin qu\u2019ils courent devant son char;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.12","name":"1 Samuel 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.10","name":"1 Samuel 8:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.12","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:12","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>il s\u2019en fera des chefs de mille et des chefs de cinquante, et il les emploiera \u00e0 labourer ses terres, \u00e0 r\u00e9colter ses moissons, \u00e0 fabriquer ses armes de guerre et l\u2019attirail de ses chars.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.13","name":"1 Samuel 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.11","name":"1 Samuel 8:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.13","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:13","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Il prendra vos filles, pour en faire des parfumeuses, des cuisini\u00e8res et des boulang\u00e8res.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.14","name":"1 Samuel 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.12","name":"1 Samuel 8:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.14","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:14","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Il prendra la meilleure partie de vos champs, de vos vignes et de vos oliviers, et la donnera \u00e0 ses serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.15","name":"1 Samuel 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.13","name":"1 Samuel 8:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.15","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:15","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Il prendra la d\u00eeme du produit de vos semences et de vos vignes, et la donnera \u00e0 ses serviteurs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.16","name":"1 Samuel 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.14","name":"1 Samuel 8:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.16","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:16","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Il prendra vos serviteurs et vos servantes, vos meilleurs b\u0153ufs et vos \u00e2nes, et s\u2019en servira pour ses travaux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.17","name":"1 Samuel 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.15","name":"1 Samuel 8:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.17","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:17","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Il prendra la d\u00eeme de vos troupeaux, et vous-m\u00eames serez ses esclaves.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.18","name":"1 Samuel 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.16","name":"1 Samuel 8:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.18","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:18","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Et alors vous crierez contre votre roi que vous vous serez choisi, mais l\u2019\u00c9ternel ne vous exaucera point.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.19","name":"1 Samuel 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.17","name":"1 Samuel 8:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.19","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:19","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le peuple refusa d\u2019\u00e9couter la voix de Samuel. Non! Dirent-ils, mais il y aura un roi sur nous,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.20","name":"1 Samuel 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.18","name":"1 Samuel 8:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.20","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:20","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>et nous aussi nous serons comme toutes les nations; notre roi nous jugera il marchera \u00e0 notre t\u00eate et conduira nos guerres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.21","name":"1 Samuel 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.19","name":"1 Samuel 8:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.21","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:21","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.008.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Samuel, apr\u00e8s avoir entendu toutes les paroles du peuple, les redit aux oreilles de l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.22","name":"1 Samuel 8:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.20","name":"1 Samuel 8:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.22","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 8:22","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.008.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.009.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.8.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Samuel: \u00c9coute leur voix, et \u00e9tablis un roi sur eux. Et Samuel dit aux hommes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Allez-vous-en chacun dans sa ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8","name":"1 Samuel 8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.9.1","name":"1 Samuel 9:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.9.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.8.21","name":"1 Samuel 8:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.8.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb23f4559.81884389');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb23f4559.81884389\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb23f4559.81884389","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb23f4559.81884389'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb23f4559.81884389\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}